title: Beautiful Lynnwood 4 Bedroom House
posting_body: ['Available for viewing and renting from July 26th.', 'Beautiful & New Lynnwood 4 Bedroom House for a family only (No shared rooms).', 'This 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath house has great location near shopping and restaurants.', 'Quiet, safe, 3 minutes out to I-5 and 405 and HW 99.', 'Modern Designs, with hard wood floors on main level, great room with lovely kitchen, granite countertops.', 'Upstairs all carpeted, large master suite with large walk-in closet and full bathroom.', 'One additional bedroom with walk-in closets.', 'One very big bedroom and one small bedroom shared full bath and down the hallway a nice sized laundry room.', 'Half bathroom downstairs.', 'Home well maintained.', '1,907 square feet of living space.', 'Spacious 2 story home.', 'Open floor plan living, dining, and kitchen boasts granite countertops with 3 windows overlooking the backyard with a little nice garden.', 'Driveway for up to 2 cars, plus a 2-car garage.', 'A lot of space for parking on the street.', 'Meticulously maintained by one owner.', 'Community features sidewalks, with no through traffic.', 'This home was just built in April 2015.', 'Central heating, washer/dryer, microwave, oven, refrigerator provided.', '5 min to a bus stop with ONLY 1 bus to Alderwood mall (113), Lynnwood Transit Center (113), Ashway P&R (880), Seattle, etc.', "5 min to groceries (Safeway, Bartell's...), Alderwood Mall, Costco, HW 99 and freeway I-5, I-405.", 'Credit check must be approved and paid by renter.', 'Renter pays for W/S/G and Internet.', 'Security Deposit is $3050', 'Text Tam', 'show contact info', 'for application link on Zillow.']
